{"tid":1802470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨上水「和你Shop」20人被捕　檢雷射筆鐵錘","createTime":"2019-12-29T13:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T13:31:59.000Z","uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb34edbfaf778e27964affbe8c01051d206f898","tid":1802470,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"昨日(28日)下午有約150名示威者在未有按法例要求通知警方的情況下，在上水廣場一帶聚集，並進入商場店舖擾亂秩序，阻礙正常商業活動。<br />\n警方採取行動，於上址共拘捕18男2女，年齡介乎13至34歲，涉嫌非法集結。其中4名年齡介乎16至27歲男子，亦分別涉嫌阻礙警務人員執行職務及襲警被捕。警員另在一名18歲男子及一名14歲女童身上檢獲雷射筆、噴漆及鐵錘，他們分別涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途及藏有攻擊性武器被捕。案件交由大埔警區重案組跟進，被捕人士正被扣查。行動中，5名男警務人員遇襲受傷，他們清醒被送往那打素醫院治理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2nszf0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2nszf0f.png&h=3d9bae9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係要變陣喇，唔係變咗預約扣捕送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d897a7e943a68a3d7fda92663feb698b4de3fa91","tid":1802470,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"老屈都得啦  睇直播唔見有喎"},{"pid":"e93e6a579ef0648b132f452b2abe2e14f267f6de","tid":1802470,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d897a7e943a68a3d7fda92663feb698b4de3fa91","tid":1802470,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"老屈都得啦  睇直播唔見有喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kQEr9D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kQEr9D.png&h=cb96f4a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影相就見到揸住個槍柄"},{"pid":"66dbcaa585844a12f6e835ee0e4be43ffb126369","tid":1802470,"uid":30476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e93e6a579ef0648b132f452b2abe2e14f267f6de","tid":1802470,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d897a7e943a68a3d7fda92663feb698b4de3fa91","tid":1802470,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:15:17.000Z